            This is a very important game for Atletico as anything but a win in this game is going to demote morale and make them lose the fear factor their opponents usually have when playing against them. To add to that, Sevilla is coming to Calderon full of confidence and having notched up 4 wins and a draw in the first 5 games of the La Liga. Atletico are in for a hell of a week!
